'''阿妮塔·萨克伊西恩'''（{{lang-en|Anita Sarkeesian}}，{{bd|1983年|||}}）是一位来自加拿大的美国[[女性主义|女性主义]]媒体评论人。她生于[[多伦多|多伦多]]附近的一个[[亚美尼亚|亚美尼亚]]移民家庭，后移居[[加利福尼亚|加利福尼亚]]。<ref name=Moore>{{cite news |title= Woman's call to end video game misogyny sparks vicious online attacks |last= Moore |first= Oliver |url= http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/womans-call-to-end-video-game-misogyny-sparks-vicious-online-attacks/article4405585/ |newspaper= The Globe and Mail |date= July 11, 2012 |accessdate= March 13, 2014 |archive-date= 2017-05-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170511025245/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/womans-call-to-end-video-game-misogyny-sparks-vicious-online-attacks/article4405585/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://colorlines.com/archives/2012/12/watch_aris_bakhtanians_deconstruct_sexism_in_gaming.html |title= Watch Anita Sarkeesian Deconstruct Sexism in Gaming |last1= Rivas |first1= Jorge |date= December 13, 2012 |website= [[ColorLines|ColorLines]] |accessdate= March 13, 2014 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20121216040933/http://colorlines.com/archives/2012/12/watch_aris_bakhtanians_deconstruct_sexism_in_gaming.html |archive-date= 2012-12-16 |dead-url= yes }}</ref><ref name=Greenhouse13>{{cite news |last= Greenhouse |first= Emily |date= August 1, 2013 |title= Twitter's Free Speech Problem |url= http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/elements/2013/08/how-free-should-speech-be-on-twitter.html |newspaper= [[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]] |location=  |publisher=  |accessdate= March 24, 2014 |archive-date= 2014-07-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140702154937/http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/elements/2013/08/how-free-should-speech-be-on-twitter.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>她在[[加州州立大学诺斯里奇分校|加州州立大学诺斯里奇分校]]获传播学学士学位，2010年于[[约克大学|约克大学]]获社会及政治科学硕士学位。<ref name = "FemFreqAbout">{{cite web | last = Sarkeesian |first = Anita | title = About | work = Feminist Frequency | url =http://www.feministfrequency.com/about/ | accessdate = March 13, 2014}}</ref><ref name=Kolhatkar>{{cite news |last= Kolhatkar |first= Sheelah |date= November 26, 2014 |title= The Gaming Industry's Greatest Adversary Is Just Getting Started |url= http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2014-11-26/anita-sarkeesian-battles-sexism-in-games-gamergate-harassment |newspaper= [[Bloomberg_Businessweek|Bloomberg Businessweek]] |location=  |accessdate= December 4, 2014 |archive-date= 2014-11-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141126142636/http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2014-11-26/anita-sarkeesian-battles-sexism-in-games-gamergate-harassment |dead-url= no }}</ref>

萨克伊西恩建立了个人网站“女性主义频率”，并发布了一系列影片讨论《[[侠盗猎车手|侠盗猎车手]]》、《[[刺客信条|刺客信条]]》等畅销游戏中对于女性的表现。她搜集了多个游戏中的女性形象，认为有的是隐晦的被贬低，而有许多图像则是过度性感、并常常让女性承受极度暴力，有时这些角色遇害时玩家还能得到奖励。她们常常被表现为柔弱的落难女子，或者背景的简单点缀。萨克伊西恩的这些言论也引来了不少骚扰，包括以她名义所开的假账户、传假信息，并把她的头像PS到色情电影剧照上，以及其他各种普通的威胁骚扰；同時，阿妮塔亦備受遊戲玩家及網民批評其論證缺乏說服力，有著[[邏輯謬誤|邏輯謬誤]]，如[[採櫻桃謬誤|採櫻桃謬誤]]—刻意挑選有柔弱女子或使女角色死亡時玩家會得到獎項的遊戲。<ref>Sheelah Kolhatkar. 视频游戏对女性做了什么？——一位评论家如何在试图挑战一份250亿美元的产业. 商业周刊中文版. 2015年第2期. 页75-79.</ref>

